#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "2,000 parents<br/> brought their kid to our nursery."
msgstr "2,000 rodziców<br/> przyprowadziło swoje dzieci do naszego żłobka."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        For every kid"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Dla każdego dziecka"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Open-door policy"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Polityka otwartych drzwi"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Our mission"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Nasza misja"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid "A little place <br/>of paradise"
msgstr "Mały kawałek <br/>raju"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "About us"
msgstr "O nas"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Activities"
msgstr "Czynności"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"All activities are planned to meet each child’s individual needs. This "
"approach will help your child to develop to the best of their ability."
msgstr ""
"Wszystkie zajęcia są zaplanowane tak, aby zaspokoić indywidualne potrzeby "
"każdego dziecka. Takie podejście pomoże dziecku rozwijać się najlepiej jak "
"potrafi."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Skontaktuj się z nami"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__display_name
msgid "Display Name"
msgstr "Nazwa wyświetlana"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_call_to_action
msgid "Entrust us with your children and go to work with peace of mind"
msgstr "Powierz nam swoje dzieci i idź do pracy ze spokojem ducha"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Events"
msgstr "Wydarzenia"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model.fields,field_description:theme_kiddo.field_theme_utils__id
msgid "ID"
msgstr "ID"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Our aim is to make the early years of your child’s life as enjoyable, "
"rewarding and positive as possible."
msgstr ""
"Naszym celem jest uczynienie wczesnych lat życia dziecka tak przyjemnymi, "
"satysfakcjonującymi i pozytywnymi, jak to tylko możliwe."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_banner
msgid ""
"Our goal is to create a safe and nurturing environment for your child to "
"learn and grow. We believe that every child is unique and should be treated "
"as such."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Our team"
msgstr "Nasz zespół"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid "Our team is composed of experienced nursery nurses."
msgstr "Nasz zespół składa się z doświadczonych opiekunek dziecięcych."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Playground"
msgstr "Plac zabaw"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_kiddo.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Narzędzia motywu"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_image_text
msgid ""
"They will propose to your children educational activities, playful, varied "
"and adapted to the stage of development."
msgstr ""
"Zaproponują dzieciom zabawne, zróżnicowane i dostosowane do etapu rozwoju "
"zajęcia edukacyjne."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_product_list
msgid "Visit us"
msgstr "Odwiedź nas"

#. module: theme_kiddo
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_kiddo.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"You are welcome to come and see the nursery and meet the team at any time "
"convenient to you."
msgstr ""
"Zapraszamy do odwiedzenia żłobka i spotkania się z zespołem w dogodnym dla "
"siebie czasie."

#. module: theme_kiddo
#. odoo-javascript
#: code:addons/theme_kiddo/static/src/js/tour.js:0
msgid "width"
msgstr "szerokość"
